/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Created:     17 March 2011 by cnwrs2

Purpose:     Used in the JRW
        
Change Date	Who		Reason

------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
vars

begin
	return self.dateTime.date();
epilog

end;</source>
